- 協助開發用的插件
https://github.com/thymeleaf/thymeleaf-extras-eclipse-plugin

- install step:
In Eclipse, go to Help >> Install New Software... then either use the update site URL, or download a ZIP archive of the plugin from SourceForge:

Update site URL: http://www.thymeleaf.org/eclipse-plugin-update-site/
ZIP file downloads: https://bintray.com/thymeleaf/downloads/thymeleaf-extras-eclipse-plugin/

- use step:
1. Declaring the dialect namespace and prefix in your HTML files

This is the easiest method and you may have already done this to keep the XML validator happy:
-----------------------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
......
-------------------------------------------------